    <p class="heading-eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1 class="heading-1" id="about-title">Experience & Leadership</h1>

    <h2 class="heading-2">Professional Experience</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Senior Data Scientist, National Analytics Lab</strong> (2020–present)
        <p>
          Led AI/ML products for public policy analytics, built governance-ready ML pipelines, and
          scaled dashboards for senior stakeholders.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Data Science Lead, SmartCity Insights</strong> (2017–2020)
        <p>
          Designed a city-wide dashboarding platform on Tableau and Power BI ingesting 300+ daily streams.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="heading-2">Education</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Master of Science in Data Science (Thesis: Scalable ML for Socioeconomic Forecasting)</li>
      <li>BSc in Computer Science and Economics</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="heading-2">Certifications</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Microsoft Certified: Azure AI Engineer Associate</li>
      <li>Tableau Desktop Specialist</li>
      <li>Google Cloud Professional Data Engineer</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="heading-2">Selected Achievements</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Published ResearchGate study on ethical AI for public sector planning</li>
      <li>Presented at global Data For Good conference (2024)</li>
      <li>Led cross-functional team to reduce reporting latency by 65% in production dashboards</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
